Package org.JE.JE2.Objects

Class GameObject

java.lang.Object
org.JE.JE2.Objects.GameObject
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public final class GameObject extends Object implements Serializable
JE2 - GameObject GameObjects are the base for everything you see in JE2. Every object possesses a Transform (pos, rot, scale). GameObjects can have scripts attached to them to add additional behaviour. GameObjects should have a default constructor if you want them to work with save/load features.
